,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":32}],"windowDisplayName":"록","body":"우와~! 엄청 맛있어 보이는 과자가 가득하네요~!\n앗, 고구마 쿠키도 있네요!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":32,"voiceId":"event133-01-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"마스킹","body":"오, 좋은데. 탄산하고 팝콘도 있어?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event133-01-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"레이야","body":"탄산이라면 있어.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"nnf02","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"event133-01-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"츄츄","body":"Wait, Wait! 너희 잠깐만!\n어째서 Home theater 분위기를 내는 거야!?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event133-01-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"츄츄","body":"지금부터 볼 것은 지금까지의 라이브 영상을 편집한 종합편이야.\n다음 단독 라이브의 중요한 Key point라고!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event133-01-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"마스킹","body":"알고 있다니까.\n지금까지의 라이브 영상이 나오면서 관객들이 들떠있을 때\n신곡을 쿵~!! 하고 화려하게 내놓는 작전이잖아?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event133-01-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":32}],"windowDisplayName":"록","body":"으으~~ 그렇게 하면 무조건 끓어오를 거예요!\n벌써부터 두근거림이 멈추지 않아요!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"kime02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":32,"voiceId":"event133-01-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":34}],"windowDisplayName":"파레오","body":"게다가 이번에는 라이브뿐만이 아니라 생중계도 있으니까요♪\n전 세계의 여러분께 신곡을 선보이는 거예요~","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":34,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":34,"voiceId":"event133-01-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"레이야","body":"과연 츄츄. 이번에도 의욕적이네.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"nnf05","expressionName":"smile02","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"event133-01-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"츄츄","body":"Of course!\n이 영상은 단독 라이브를 더욱 열광시키기 위한 기폭제야!\n그러니까 들떠있을 게 아니라 제대로 체크를……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"kime02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event133-01-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"레이야","body":"딱히 들떠있는 건 아닌데……\n아, 여기 육포 주먹밥도 있어, 츄츄.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"event133-01-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":34}],"windowDisplayName":"파레오","body":"츄츄 님, 같이 문어 비엔나 드실래요?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":34,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":34,"voiceId":"event133-01-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"마스킹","body":"오~ 문어 비엔나다카이.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event133-01-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"레이야","body":"또 그거야? 마스키는 정말 끈질기네.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"event133-01-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":32}],"windowDisplayName":"록","body":"후후후, 츄츄 씨도 그런 곳에 서 있지 말고\n여기로 오세요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":32,"voiceId":"event133-01-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"츄츄","body":"하아…… 완전히 들떠있잖아……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event133-01-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"츄츄","body":"뭐 좋아……\n그러면 시작한다! It's show time!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event133-01-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"츄츄","body":"Sweet! Excellent! Unstoppable!\n완벽한걸! 그야말로 최강의 영상이야!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event133-01-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":34}],"windowDisplayName":"파레오","body":"네 츄츄 님! RAS 이즈 최강이에요~♪","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":34,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":34,"voiceId":"event133-01-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"마스킹","body":"엄~~청 좋은 영상이잖아!!\n이거면 힘껏 날뛰어야겠어!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event133-01-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"레이야","body":"록? 왜 그래?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"event133-01-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":32}],"windowDisplayName":"록","body":"아, 아뇨, 영상은 엄청 멋졌는데요……\n제가 연주하는 부분을 보니까 역시 부끄러워서요……\n으으…… 익숙해지지 않아요~~","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":32,"voiceId":"event133-01-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"레이야","body":"후후, 부끄러워할 거 없어, 록.\n엄청 멋졌어.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"event133-01-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":32}],"windowDisplayName":"록","body":"아, 아, 아니에요! 레이야씨야말로 멋져요!!\n특히 그 「날뛸 준비 됐어?」라고 말하는 부분이\n엄청 멋졌어요~~!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":32,"voiceId":"event133-01-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":34}],"windowDisplayName":"파레오","body":"맞아요~!\n파레오도 그 MC를 들으면 매번 짜릿해요~~♪","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":34,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":34,"voiceId":"event133-01-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"레이야","body":"둘 다 고마워.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"event133-01-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":32}],"windowDisplayName":"록","body":"저기, 언제 물어보고 싶었는데요,\n그 MC는 츄츄 씨가 생각해 낸 건가요?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":32,"voiceId":"event133-01-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"츄츄","body":"No, 그건…… 레이야가 스스로 꺼낸 거야.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event133-01-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"레이야","body":"응. 아마도 처음 RAS로서 노래했을 때였나?\n공연장 열기를 받는 사이에…… 자연스레 입에서 나왔어.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"event133-01-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":32}],"windowDisplayName":"록","body":"에엥~!\n저라면 그런 멋진 대사가 바로 나오지 않을 거예요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":32,"voiceId":"event133-01-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"레이야","body":"그때는 무아몽중 상태여서 별로 제대로 기억나지 않아.\n왠지 내가 내가 아닌 것 같았거든……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"event133-01-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"츄츄","body":"그때의 레이야는 그야말로 Unstoppable!\n내재된 강렬한 감정이 날뛰기 시작하는 멋진 퍼포먼스였어!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event133-01-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":32}],"windowDisplayName":"록","body":"우와~ 왠지 전설 에피소드 같네요!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":32,"voiceId":"event133-01-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"츄츄","body":"레이야는 멋진 보컬이야.\n내가 원하는 Order대로 반드시 성공시키거든.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event133-01-037","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"레이야","body":"츄츄……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"event133-01-038","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"츄츄","body":"그렇기에 레이야한테는……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event133-01-039","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"마스킹","body":"좋아, 영상은 완벽하군.\n그러면 오늘부터 드디어 신곡 연습 시작이네!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event133-01-040","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"츄츄","body":"그래, 그거 말인데.\n신곡에 대해서 너희 의견, 아이디어를 내줬으면 좋겠어.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event133-01-041","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":900000}],"windowDisplayName":"일동","body":"……엥?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":33,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":900000,"voiceId":"event133-01-042","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"츄츄","body":"What? 뭐야, 너희 전부 어리둥절한 표정인데.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event133-01-043","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"마스킹","body":"아니…… 놀랍잖아.\n츄츄가 그런 말을 하다니 처음 있는 일 아니야?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event133-01-044","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"츄츄","body":"당연하지, Best하고 최강인 신곡을 만들었다고 자부하고 있어.\n하지만 그만큼 너희 연주 실력도 신뢰하고 있어.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"kime02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event133-01-045","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"츄츄","body":"신곡을 더욱 최강으로 만들기 위해서 너희 의견을 듣고 싶어.\n물론 검토할 가치가 있는 의견이라면 말이지만!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"serious02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event133-01-046","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":34}],"windowDisplayName":"파레오","body":"신뢰……!\n츄츄 님께서 그렇게 말씀해 주시다니……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":34,"motionName":"happy01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":34,"voiceId":"event133-01-047","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":34}],"windowDisplayName":"파레오","body":"파레오는 감동했어요!\n츄츄 님의 그 신뢰를 절대로 배신하지 않을게요!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":34,"motionName":"shame02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":34,"voiceId":"event133-01-048","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"마스킹","body":"그러면 말해도 되지? 악보 받았을 때부터 신경 쓰였던 건데……\n역시 후렴에서 흥을 더 내려면\n더 임팩트가 있는 게 짜릿할 것 같은데.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event133-01-049","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":32}],"windowDisplayName":"록","body":"맞아요!\n그 부분이라면 저도 써 보고 싶은 이펙트가 있어요!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":32,"voiceId":"event133-01-050","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"마스킹","body":"이봐 잠깐만 록.\n나도 후렴 앞 분위기 잡는 거, 한번 시험해보고 싶어.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event133-01-051","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":34}],"windowDisplayName":"파레오","body":"그러면 파레오한테도 아이디어가……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motio